<p>Thanks to the following (and if I missed anyone, lemme know!):</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;">kinchtheknifeblade</a></span> for looking at so many versions of this and hopefully not being annoyed every time I poked her about it again, as well as helping me with info on many of the characters such as Jude, JJ, Esther, polaricecraps, harmpit, hetcopogg, and gaycopmp4.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(617958); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=617958&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="Communism will win" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=617958)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(617958); return false;">Communism will win</a></span> for making me keep working on it even when I thought I was done, and making it better as a result, as well as helping me with various characters such as Jude and harmpit.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scarhaver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2838541); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2838541&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="scarhaver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2838541)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scarhaver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2838541); return false;">scarhaver</a></span> for helping me with bones, JJ, and hetcopogg.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/joreth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1370009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1370009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="Joreth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1370009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/joreth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1370009); return false;">Joreth</a></span> for verifying that all the character attributes I forced onto his characters was good and correct, such as kkrule, TrainerDP, talman_corvett, opossum, tiedyeduck, and DonDeLillo.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/monkeysky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1390998); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1390998&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="Monkeysky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1390998)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/monkeysky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1390998); return false;">Monkeysky</a></span> for coming up with all the ideas for FunkoPopFan1, as well as general critique.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doormaker" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1749664); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1749664&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="doormaker" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1749664)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doormaker" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1749664); return false;">doormaker</a></span> for coming up with all the ideas for fallout_meta.txt, as well as general critique.</li>
<li>Ky for making goodpostskitty even better than she already was when pointing out a typo I had, as well as general critique.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="Aiden Eldritch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Aiden Eldritch</a></span> for tone.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ch00bakka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1238719); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1238719&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="ch00bakka" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1238719)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ch00bakka" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1238719); return false;">ch00bakka</a></span> for letting me tie CommunismAnarchismNihilism into their SCP-2573.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1349098); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1349098&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="Jekeled" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1349098)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jekeled" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1349098); return false;">Jekeled</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fenton-st" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3026684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3026684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="fenton-st" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3026684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fenton-st" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3026684); return false;">fenton-st</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dolphinslugchugger" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1969477); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1969477&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="DolphinSlugchugger" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1969477)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dolphinslugchugger" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1969477); return false;">DolphinSlugchugger</a></span> for generally positive feedback.</li>
</ul>
<p>The idea for a group of interest dossier came to mind when reading <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eric-h" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(474585); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=474585&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1496000111" alt="eric_h" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=474585)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eric-h" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(474585); return false;">eric_h</a></span>'s great <a href="/poi-dark">Person of Interest - Mr. Dark</a> tale. I wanted to do something similar but for a group of interest. For months, I've been wondering which one to do one on, as I could imagine this sort of format could be real boring for some groups; only a few come to mind that would make it a colorful read. And, well, GAW has been a thing and I've come around from hating it so I decided to do this one.</p>
<p>In writing this, I've come to like the group a lot more (not quite in positive territory, but much closer). I think it's hard to see or imagine, but there are some pretty complex characters here that go deeper than &quot;memes&quot; or what have you. Also; having a group be entirely US-centric and US-focused doesn't feel right, even (and maybe especially) though they're political and mostly are a marginalized group of people. You don't need to live in just America to have your opinions and feelings on such a thing. Hopefully this does a decent job illuminating everything said above. Hopefully you all like it as well!</p>
<p>I added new characters to it and more or less made up my own shit. It's canon. Right now, this document is a snapshot in time and I'm not sure I want this page specifically to either be an open collaboration or updated as stuff gets posted. I'll see what happens and update of my own accord.</p>
<p>References in the new names:</p>
