<p>Author Questions:</p>
<p>1) Is it Good Posts Kitty or Good Post Skitty?<br />
2) How do you suppose oppressed reality benders manage to find each other and form a bond and a community?<br />
3) What would the Threat Levels for other Groups of Interest look like?<br />
4) What's Three6serpent's deal?</p>
<p>What I Listened to While Writing: Lucio Battisti's Anima latina, Love's Forever Changes.</p>

