			<div class="content" id="post-content-2853795">
									

<p>Hey Decibelles, could I add Kektagon from 3108 to this dossier? Made a write up here using the info in the article and my own thoughts on him. Eventually I intend to write the blacked out skips, but they aren't super high on my list of priorities:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Nathan Pierce (PoI-6897):</strong> AKA <strong>Kektagon</strong>. 19. Low level reality bender known for creating anomalies affected by the cognition of their users or viewers. Dislikes serious topics and tends to limit his chat interaction to attempts at humor. Shares the pacifist views of GAW's founders, but lack of forethought has resulted in some of his creations possessing dangerous applications. Creator of SCP-████, SCP-████, and <a href="/scp-3108">SCP-3108</a>.</li>
</ul>

